@hypebeastwatches: @hublot has dropped a pair of limited timepieces to celebrate its success in recreating gold crystals, the rarest form of raw gold found in nature. The expertly crated crystals are applied to a black dial, set in place under 20 layers of transparent lacquer, and housed inside Hublot’s Spirit of Big Bang case. 39mm and 42mm versions are now available via Hublot, priced at $28,400 USD and $29,500 USD respectively.⁠⁠

#hypeAF: @polaroid has introduced its most versatile product camera yet with the Now+, a reimagined instant camera with new upgrades to enhance your creativity. The new camera features aperture priority and tripod mode functionalities allowing creators to experiment with the depth of field and long exposures. For this edition, we’re featuring @liverpoolfc captain @jhenderson and his activism efforts - whether it’s his work with The Cybersmile Foundation, his #PlayersTogether initiative, or simply the motivation to always lead by example. Read how Henderson is becoming a role model with a passion and purpose via the link in bio.⁠⁠

node.text:
@hypebeaststyle: @kenzo appoints @nigo as its new Creative Director, who will succeed Felipe Oliveria Baptist. The @bape_japan and @humanmade founder will begin his new role on September 20, and is expected to unveil his first collection for both men and women during Paris Fashion Week in January 2022. "I was born in the year that Takada Kenzo san opened his first store in Paris. We both graduated from the same fashion school in Tokyo. In 1993, the year that KENZO joined the LVMH Group, I started my career in fashion," NIGO states in the official announcement. ⁠
Photo: NIGO

Located in Ashdown Forest, the “Bearbnb” sleeps up to four guests and is hosted by Kim Raymond, the artist behind the series for over 30 years. Head over to the link in bio for more details.⁠⁠
